<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Sign in as council admin</h3>

<ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-list--spaced">
  <li>
    <strong>Go to the sign-in page</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Click <strong>"Sign in"</strong> in the top-right corner of the FixMyStreet homepage,
      or navigate directly to <code>/auth</code> on your FixMyStreet URL.
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Enter your admin credentials</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Use the <strong>AdminUsername</strong> and <strong>AdminPassword</strong> from Step 1
      (the CloudFormation Outputs tab).
    </p>
  </li>

  <li>
    <strong>Navigate to the council reports view</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Once signed in, navigate to <code>/reports/NDX+Demo+Council</code> on your FixMyStreet URL.
      This shows all reports submitted to the NDX Demo Council on a single map view.
    </p>
    <div class="govuk-inset-text">
      <p class="govuk-body">
        <strong>Tip:</strong> You can also reach this page by clicking "All reports" in the navigation,
        then selecting the council area.
      </p>
    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

